org.kurento.client

Interface ZBarFilter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Filter, KurentoObject, MediaElement, MediaObject

    public interface ZBarFilter
extends Filter
    This filter detects QR codes in a video feed. When a code is found, the filter raises a :rom:evnt:`CodeFound` event.
